data.text:
New York: Warner Books, 1996. First Edition, First Printing. Octavo; 560 pages; Dustjacket spine Blue with Silver and White text; Quarter bound in blue cloth with navy blue paper boards and silver lettering on spine; Dustjacket protected by mylar cover. Dust jacket has minor edge wear and shelf wear. Boards strong, minor edge wear and shelf wear, color fading along edges. Text block has photo of previous owner with Aldrin on reverse of front endpaper. Inscribed by Buzz Aldrin "To Irene, Happy 50" on title page; Shelved Case 8, EF Consignment.

1338412

Shelved Dupont Bookstore
